<h1>📋 About This Application</h1>

<div class="info-card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h3>🎯 Purpose</h3>
    <p>This is a demonstration ASP.NET Core application for testing IIS deployment, authentication, and monitoring on Windows servers. Perfect for observability testing with tools like Datadog!</p>
</div>

<div class="info-card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h3>🔧 Technology Stack</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>ASP.NET Core 9.0</li>
        <li>MVC Pattern with Razor Views</li>
        <li>Cookie-based Authentication</li>
        <li>Built-in Health Checks</li>
        <li>Logging & Monitoring APIs</li>
        <li>No External Dependencies</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h3>✨ Features</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>✅ Simple Authentication (admin/password)</li>
        <li>✅ Protected Admin Dashboard</li>
        <li>✅ Auto-healthcheck every 30 seconds</li>
        <li>✅ Monitoring endpoints for observability</li>
        <li>✅ Self-contained IIS deployment</li>
        <li>✅ System information display</li>
        <li>✅ Responsive modern UI</li>
        <li>✅ HTTP-only (no SSL required)</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h3>🔐 Authentication</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Username:</strong> admin</li>
        <li><strong>Password:</strong> password</li>
        <li><strong>Features:</strong> Protected dashboard, session management</li>
        <li><strong>Type:</strong> Cookie-based authentication</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <h3>📊 Monitoring & Observability</h3>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>/health</strong> - Built-in health check endpoint</li>
        <li><strong>/api/healthcheck</strong> - Detailed health data (JSON)</li>
        <li><strong>/api/metrics</strong> - Application metrics (JSON)</li>
        <li><strong>Auto-monitoring:</strong> Healthcheck every 30 seconds</li>
        <li><strong>Logging:</strong> Structured logging for all endpoints</li>
        <li><strong>Perfect for:</strong> Datadog, New Relic, Application Insights</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="info-card">
    <h3>🚀 Deployment Requirements</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Windows Server with IIS</li>
        <li>.NET 9.0 Runtime</li>
        <li>ASP.NET Core Module V2</li>
        <li>That's it!</li>
    </ul>
</div>
